label: lsbds-rho-1
description: Conditions, under which LSBDS degenerates into CRBD.
model:
var mu_0 = epsilon * lambda_0
	var nsamples = 100
	var ret = simLSBDS( tree, lambda_0, mu_0, eta, DistLambda, DistMu, rho )
	var max_M = 10000
	var M = M_lsbdsGoesUndetected( tree.age, lambda_0, mu_0, eta, DistLambda, DistMu, rho, max_M )
	factor(Math.log(M))
	return ret
